WEBVTT

00:03:25.423 --> 00:03:30.052
There are no restrictions
that could ever be so rigorous

00:03:30.076 --> 00:03:35.585
to stop the wave of migration
that has determined our human history.

00:03:35.609 --> 00:03:38.474
Before border controls can be tightened

00:03:38.498 --> 00:03:41.462
and new visa restrictions imposed,

00:03:41.486 --> 00:03:44.031
countries that have long received migrants

00:03:44.055 --> 00:03:47.373
should engage in a more open discussion.

00:03:47.397 --> 00:03:52.273
That is the only practical start
for reconciling, finally,

00:03:53.217 --> 00:03:55.563
a legacy of exploitation,

00:03:56.713 --> 00:03:58.229
slavery,

00:03:58.253 --> 00:03:59.653
colonialism

00:03:59.677 --> 00:04:01.457
and imperialism,